Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of automation and computer intelligence to support complex human decisions in managing large and distributed systems in the Cloud and IoT era. This suggests a focus on artificial intelligence and software engineering, which are covered by the cs.AI and cs.SE sub-categories. The paper also discusses the challenge of handling large amounts of data and providing real-time feedback, which suggests a focus on distributed computing (cs.DC) and systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the use of models and techniques for root cause analysis, which suggests a focus on databases (cs.DB) for storing and analyzing data.
